properties.General Description: Exposed Pleistocene reefs along northern part of the Sudan coast. Location gives site of exposed section rather than full extent of deposit. Four diff coral reef zones have been identified and assigned to MIS9, MIS7, MIS5 (e and a). Also present in places along this coastline is alluvial sediment which overlies the MIS9 reef and, in a few locations, MIS1 beach rock

Also present in places along this coastline is alluvial sediment which overlies the MIS9 reef and, in a few locations, MIS1 beach rock
